snippet.title: Let's Fix This Universe! | Steven Universe: Attack The Light | Ep.1
snippet.description:
Today we learn the basics of Steven Universe Attack The Light

Catch a glimpse of the new Steven Universe mobile game “Attack the Light.” The Gems have their hands full when Steven accidentally releases an entire army of light! Hey, even light has its dark side. Team up as Steven, Garnet, Amethyst, and Pearl to battle a full spectrum of nasty monsters! Each Gem has a unique set of powers to unleash and awesome abilities to upgrade. Get ready to Attack the Light! This is one magic mission you won’t want to miss
